Replicaset is an wrapper on top of a POD 

it makes pod resilient (மீளுந்திறன்=== again comes back ) , if any of the pod crashes out of 3 pods let say 2 pods crashed for some reasons 
Replicaset recreates those two parts to meet 3 as a disired state 

we can not create dry-run method for replicaset sicne we are creating deployment via dry-run method to create yaml fie 
and replace with replicaset in yaml file with deployment in kind 

# kubectl create deployment nginx --image=nginx:latest --replicas=3 --dry-run=client -o yaml > nginx-rs.yaml

To create replicaset via declarative methods 

# kubectl create -f nginx-rs.yaml 

#  kubectl get pods
# kubectl get replicaset

if we delete single pod it will recreate again and bring to the desired state 
# kubectl delete pod/nginx-9df9g
# kubectl get pods 

if we want to deleate all we need to delete replicaset instead of pod 
# kubectl delete rs nginx-rs













